If you are thinking by its title that this is a classic Stag film, you will be disappointed. If you are wanting a total escape into the escapades of a bunch of buddies celebrating life's events with each other and the deployment of a potential stag party stripper -- hey, this is your movie. Yes, it is base comedy but fairly well done.
